Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.95,0:00:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.73,0:00:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊  有那么多人都赶到汤乃鹭来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.45,0:00:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为县外也有人过来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.49,0:00:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了  许愿板
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.77,0:00:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题  大家可都拿着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.22,0:00:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（存钱）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.30,0:00:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多东西  不觉得放弃还太早了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.94,0:00:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（我现在到汤乃鹭了）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.28,0:00:43.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  我去接下阿孝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.53,0:00:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  要我开车送你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.93,0:00:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  你们先去雪愿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.13,0:00:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是老样子  真是个静不下来的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.52,0:00:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她这么跑掉好么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.16,0:00:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啥关系
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.19,0:01:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你写了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.74,0:01:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想成为新干线
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.60,0:01:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想成为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.17,0:01:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说我可是很现实的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.83,0:01:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和一个反面教材生活在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.06,0:01:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样  不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.35,0:01:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anything  去那边…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.76,0:01:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢…可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.24,0:02:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是say anything的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.03,0:02:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是告诉过你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.17,0:02:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  妈妈  给我买苹果糖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.79,0:02:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你开什么玩笑  要买自己买
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.00,0:02:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真小气  跟绪花一个样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.19,0:02:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 是她像我才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.74,0:02:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要五百万
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.58,0:02:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想让脚踝瘦下来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.46,0:02:24.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家只是在把烦恼发泄出来而已嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.03,0:02:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别做偷窥别人愿望这样恶趣味的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.02,0:02:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是很有意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.72,0:02:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.99,0:02:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.17,0:02:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.02,0:02:41.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（我想成为四十万翠  绪花）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.36,0:02:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.09,0:02:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像老板娘那样  对工作充满自豪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.42,0:02:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,处事态度认真  却有些孩子气
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.72,0:02:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论何时都不曾忘记自己最初的那份心意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.32,0:03:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不曾忘记最早的那个梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.80,0:03:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想成为这样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.50,0:03:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这个梦想  不是我一个人就能找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.78,0:03:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是因为有许多人的雪愿照亮了我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.54,0:03:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  输掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.27,0:03:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过正是因为如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.73,0:03:34.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才必须雪愿才行  在各种方面上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.55,0:03:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪愿？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.43,0:03:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花她不是说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.66,0:03:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪愿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.68,0:03:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你写什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.34,0:03:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.33,0:03:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只看一下下没关系啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.01,0:03:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很棒哦  小民
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.90,0:03:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.36,0:03:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行啦行啦鹤来同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.77,0:04:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不会少你一块肉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.90,0:04:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许笑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.89,0:04:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要什么紧要什么紧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.23,0:04:11.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（希望我有朝一日能够赶上彻先生  民子）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.28,0:04:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（作为一名厨师  希望能够更上一层楼  彻）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.72,0:04:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.16,0:04:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不跑得再快些  可是赶不上我的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.42,0:04:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.16,0:04:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿孝…你来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.54,0:04:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然会来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.21,0:04:34.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.66,0:04:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很合身哦  女服务员的制服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.63,0:04:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿孝…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.27,0:04:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.19,0:04:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那个…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.57,0:04:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想吃炒面！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.53,0:04:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.72,0:04:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔  来一份炒面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.21,0:04:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.22,0:05:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.84,0:05:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须好好说出来才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.56,0:05:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路边摊的炒面给人一种特别的感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.31,0:05:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.55,0:05:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平常在店里吃的还有家里做的都不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.47,0:05:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.26,0:05:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我也喜欢路边摊的炒面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.03,0:05:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿孝！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.19,0:05:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢…阿孝！  非常喜欢！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.77,0:05:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞  久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.24,0:05:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.87,0:05:48.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场祭典能把所有的愿望带往天上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.40,0:06:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.68,0:06:36.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你离开以后  我本打算一个人继续往前冲的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.15,0:06:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我错了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.12,0:06:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一个以我为梦想的外孙女
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.89,0:06:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以的话我想再一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.38,0:06:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想再一次…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.34,0:07:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来我要到儿子那边去住了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.00,0:07:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我守在锅炉前  不意间已经过了好久
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.86,0:07:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多我也该准备后事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.44,0:07:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这儿积累起来的重要回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.21,0:07:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打算一个不漏地全带到棺材里去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.80,0:07:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我由衷地感谢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.60,0:07:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向老板娘说一声谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.46,0:07:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.74,0:07:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要和孙子幸福哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.46,0:07:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.44,0:07:38.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈  我说两句可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.23,0:07:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望大家也都能听一听
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.65,0:07:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的事让我明白了一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.82,0:07:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还远远不够老练
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.55,0:07:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说妈了  就连姐姐我都赶不上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.89,0:07:53.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没法子咯  天生才能就不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.92,0:07:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.76,0:07:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.42,0:07:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我说过希望大家能跟着我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.01,0:08:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我还不是这块料
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.07,0:08:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈  你要关喜翠庄这件事…我同意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.87,0:08:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.32,0:08:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过只是暂时关门而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.61,0:08:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我绝不会让喜翠庄就此结束
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.13,0:08:17.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要多学习一些  多修炼一些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.40,0:08:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望有朝一日能够让旅馆重新开业
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.53,0:08:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.39,0:08:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到那个时候  再让我继承喜翠庄这个名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.22,0:08:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想开一家让妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.49,0:08:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让老板娘喜悦的旅馆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.98,0:08:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爷  到那时候我也会帮你一把的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.76,0:08:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莲先生  我也一起！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.14,0:08:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一样  丢下老公也要来这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.61,0:08:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是些笨蛋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.48,0:08:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs38}我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.25,0:08:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs38}诶  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.11,0:08:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子们越笨越可爱呢  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.11,0:08:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.93,0:08:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  今晚就尽情喝吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.23,0:08:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一醉方休！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.23,0:08:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.61,0:08:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你也一块喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.77,0:08:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没有成年…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么  少装可爱了  这小子…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.14,0:09:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.36,0:09:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不准长时间逗留哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.18,0:09:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想搞些什么花样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.73,0:09:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可得乖乖给我打报告
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.25,0:09:11.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.09,0:09:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要去偷窥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.97,0:09:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.80,0:09:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.65,0:09:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈  你接下来打算怎样？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.41,0:09:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是想暂时在熟人家里打扰一阵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.01,0:09:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟绪花一起来东京不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.27,0:09:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.91,0:09:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是打算留在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.26,0:09:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找一个能让我做女服务员混口饭吃的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.47,0:09:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混口饭吃？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.20,0:09:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.08,0:09:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起指使别人  自己干活更合我的性格
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.25,0:09:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.86,0:09:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要雪愿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.09,0:10:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会继续做一个讨人厌的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.20,0:10:03.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是为了你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.27,0:10:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢您  母亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.56,0:10:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.18,0:10:18.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不行不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.73,0:10:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,床单的这里不折好的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.15,0:10:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.97,0:10:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  在这么破的房间里…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.43,0:10:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还和一个有点古怪的人在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.70,0:00:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.45,0:10:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.92,0:10:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过居然是白住…总感觉挺过意不去的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.05,0:10:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.44,0:10:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别人说我很少会邀朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.96,0:10:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个个都高兴得莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.00,0:10:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这间旅馆果然超级棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.61,0:10:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅馆也是  这里工作的人也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.95,0:10:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是你找到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.17,0:10:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.33,0:10:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得所谓的归宿啊  并不是一开始就在那边的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.49,0:11:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是要自己找到  自己做出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.06,0:11:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到你我不免这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.61,0:11:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿孝…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.11,0:11:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…会找到的  我的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.36,0:11:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个归宿啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.63,0:11:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果…我的…归宿…跟你的一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.92,0:11:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.12,0:11:23.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.19,0:11:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.51,0:11:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在搞什么鬼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.20,0:11:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…这里是我的房间啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.85,0:11:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花的男朋友人好像很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.22,0:11:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  只不过优柔寡断而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.80,0:11:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然输给那种男人  彻先生真可怜…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.07,0:11:58.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多事情不是输赢能说清的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.99,0:12:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说…说的…也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.54,0:12:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.09,0:12:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没在老板娘房间里睡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.63,0:12:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜翠庄里我的归宿是这里嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.16,0:12:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是第一次摇熊铃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.66,0:12:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个季节貌似熊会出没哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.62,0:12:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷…便利店好远
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.37,0:12:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绕镇一圈的睡衣祭还将继续！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.38,0:12:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  忘了买肉包了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.58,0:12:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.75,0:12:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.08,0:12:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考虑过自己为什么会那么执着于喜翠庄呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.55,0:12:58.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为…能一直和彻先生在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.15,0:12:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.28,0:13:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然那个没错…但才不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.52,0:13:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…我的梦想…不知不觉间变了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.73,0:13:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前一心想着成为厨师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.63,0:13:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.65,0:13:18.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的我想成为喜翠庄的厨师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.03,0:13:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小民…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.57,0:13:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小民好厉害啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.80,0:13:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的梦想什么的…虽然还不是很清楚…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.66,0:13:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…我希望能再回到喜翠庄来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.25,0:13:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到这个许许多多的梦想诞生的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.43,0:13:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦想…诞生的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.28,0:13:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.16,0:13:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们以前就是在那里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.35,0:13:48.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别用以前这种过去时
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.13,0:13:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在那里  一定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.29,0:13:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.26,0:13:53.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.48,0:13:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定…在未来的某一天…就会在那里的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.03,0:14:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  慢慢来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.13,0:14:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.85,0:14:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.31,0:14:12.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.23,0:14:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜翠庄将作为汤乃鹭的历史建筑物保存下来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.64,0:14:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向这段短暂的经历告别
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.26,0:14:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向这段悠久的历史告别
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.98,0:14:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.53,0:14:30.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松前同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.89,0:14:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会给你发邮件的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.74,0:14:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对会去找你玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.21,0:14:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了  小翠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.39,0:16:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.02,0:16:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.24,0:16:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是已经走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.27,0:16:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…那个  不小心没赶上车
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.77,0:17:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离下班火车还有些时间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要好好道一声别
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.33,0:17:09.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和这里…喜翠庄告别…一声
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.02,0:17:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘您知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.27,0:17:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边木板的纹理
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.75,0:17:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么看都像是个人脸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.69,0:17:18.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.71,0:17:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边与其说是像人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.88,0:17:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次来到喜翠庄的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.53,0:17:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得这就像是故事中登场的旅馆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.27,0:17:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是不出意料
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.18,0:17:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了许多故事般的趣事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.05,0:17:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都遇上不同的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.32,0:17:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这都是因为大家都在雪愿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.13,0:17:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拼命努力的人聚集在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.65,0:17:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拼命雪愿的话  当然会发生各种各样的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.13,0:17:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写下故事的也正是大家一份一份的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.46,0:17:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以即使不在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.34,0:18:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论在哪里  一定都能创造  故事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.34,0:18:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.47,0:18:06.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.11,0:18:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.57,0:18:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天我会回到这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.09,0:18:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.46,0:18:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天会回来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候就由你来代替电六记录这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.93,0:18:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗  让我来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.53,0:18:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愿意的话就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.59,0:18:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.01,0:18:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我…由我来代替豆丁老爷继续记录
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.82,0:18:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这本业务日志
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.49,0:18:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…一定会回到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.85,0:18:48.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.04,0:18:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我等着你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.21,0:18:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.12,0:19:08.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等着你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.16,0:21:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈  到时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.89,0:21:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会面总不能迟到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.50,0:21:14.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.20,0:21:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路走好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.30,0:23:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还一定只是花蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.26,0:23:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…也正因为如此
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.21,0:23:08.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能够仰望高高在上的太阳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.87,0:23:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敞开喉咙畅饮水分
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.80,0:23:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正准备绽放呢
